370
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:30,290
He decided to get justice for his mother.

371
00:41:30,290 --> 00:41:34,550
Is that little prince planning to kill the queen?

372
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:43,760
The queen had too much power. The little prince wouldn't be able to put up a fight.

373
00:41:44,860 --> 00:41:48,230
If he wanted to overthrow the queen, he had only one option.

374
00:41:48,230 --> 00:41:50,430
What option?

375
00:41:52,560 --> 00:41:55,550
He had to become the heir to the throne of the Zixu Kingdom.

376
00:41:58,820 --> 00:42:02,820
The little prince disliked the fight for power the most.

377
00:42:02,820 --> 00:42:05,130
Because in the Zixu Kingdom,

378
00:42:05,130 --> 00:42:08,630
