384
00:42:32,220 --> 00:42:36,560
was actually a blood-filled imperial palace.

385
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:42,640
Must the little prince be that way?

386
00:42:42,640 --> 00:42:45,830
Can't he walk another path?

